&lt;ul type=&quot;disc&quot;&gt;
&lt;ul type=&quot;circle&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide expert-level knowledge and troubleshooting for electrical systems, particularly critical power installations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support the sales and engineering teams with technical insights during project planning and customer consultations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
