&lt;ul type=&quot;circle&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and maintain relatio

&lt;div class=&quot;job__header&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;job__title&quot;&gt;
&lt;div data-olk-copy-source=&quot;MessageBody&quot;&gt;We are EOLA Power, Florida&#39;s leading provider of UPS and battery system services, supporting hospitals, government, theme parks, and mission-critical facilities. Our Operations team is the command center that keeps our field engineers aligned, and our clients powered.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div data-olk-copy-source=&quot;MessageBody&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;We’re hiring a sharp, detail-driven Operations Control Specialist to elevate our scheduling, logistics, and dispatch. This role is not clerical, it’s high-accountability operations control. You’ll manage emergencies, juggle complex calendars, and make decisions that directly impact critical infrastructure.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;job__description body&quot;&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;x_elementToProof&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
