&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Operations Control&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ul data-start=&quot;1217&quot; data-end=&quot;1608&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Directly manage scheduling, dispatch, and coordination of Field Engineers across the country.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Prioritize emergencies and guarantee contractual response times are met.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Coordinate travel, equipment, and client deadlines under pressure.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Act as the&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;central hub&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;between clients, engineers, and internal departments.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Escalate and solve client issues quickly and professionally.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Operational Support&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ul data-start=&quot;1634&quot; data-end=&quot;1888&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Draft and issue service quotes based on field recommendations.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Compile and finalize Field Service Reports for client delivery.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Track parts and equipment tied to service jobs.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Support cross-department projects and ensure deadlines are met.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;What You Bring&lt;/strong&gt;
&lt;ul data-start=&quot;1914&quot; data-end=&quot;2547&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div&gt;3+ years in&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;operations scheduling, crew coordination, or dispatch&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;(airline, airport, utilities, construction, HVAC, service, or similar).&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Proven ability to handle&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;real-time logistics and emergencies&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;with multiple moving parts.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Strong judgment, prioritization, and communication skills in&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;high-stakes environments&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Comfort with complex calendars, service ticketing, and job costing.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Tech fluency: Microsoft 365, Adobe, ChatGPT, Grok and service/work order systems.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Bonus: Exposure to electrical, HVAC, UPS, or facilities service industries.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Detail-obsessed,&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;you don’t let things slip through the cracks.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
