&lt;p&gt;EOLA Power is one of the fastest-growing critical power companies in the United States and an Inc. 5000 Fastest-Growing Company (2025). We service UPS systems, batteries, and mission-critical infrastructure for hospitals, industrial facilities, municipalities, and data centers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;41&quot; data-end=&quot;139&quot;&gt;We are hiring a Sales Account Executive for an in-person, office-based role in Miami or Orlando.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;141&quot; data-end=&quot;471&quot;&gt;This role is designed for a driven, technically minded, and coachable professional who takes ownership of their results and wants to build a long-term career in the critical power industry. You should be motivated by growth, open to development, and ready to earn the opportunity to advance into a Senior Account Executive role.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;473&quot; data-end=&quot;669&quot; data-is-last-node=&quot;&quot; data-is-only-node=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;While this is an in-office position based in Miami or Orlando, we are open to high-caliber candidates located elsewhere in Florida who are willing to be aligned with our team and travel as needed.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;473&quot; data-end=&quot;669&quot; data-is-last-node=&quot;&quot; data-is-only-node=&quot;&quot;&gt;If you’re not in front of customers, you’ll be in the office working with the team, preparing to be in front of customers (if located in Orlando or Miami).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT YOU WILL DO&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Learn how to scope UPS replacements, battery upgrades, bypass systems, repairs, and PM programs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct site visits, build proposals, and manage your pipeline&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work closely with Inside Sales, Contracting, Engineering, and Field Service teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build long-term relationships across healthcare, industrial, municipal, and commercial markets&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain disciplined follow-up, organization, and CRM accuracy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;IN-PERSON EXPECTATION (IMPORTANT)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role is &lt;strong&gt;office-based&lt;/strong&gt; because it accelerates your development.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You are expected to be &lt;strong&gt;in the office&lt;/strong&gt; unless you are:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Meeting clients&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Visiting sites&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Attending tradeshows or events&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Traveling your territory&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Engaging in revenue-producing activity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you&#39;re not in front of customers, you&#39;re with us, learning, preparing, and building toward being in front of customers.&lt;/p&gt;
